    "I chose the time of the day when I was in better shape.",
    "That was something I thought was very nice, you know, not having to connect at a fixed time.\"",
    "[INT 15] • Staying engaged • \"It went really well.",
    "Then, you know, you'd scroll, then you'd click, scroll, click, so that, you know, it kept you present; you had to be there...",
    "It's not like a video you start and then lose focus."
